空間係3維<br />\n第四維係無形既時間<br />\n如果無第四維時間<br />\n你同我只會係永恆不變既死物"},{"pid":"521cda78958f07b4c2f91671521b41f903ef03af","tid":918126,"uid":163024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_8PYYnuoZP8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_8PYYnuoZP8&d=kPlvPdLcVkc%2Fw3cbopP%2FZpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=184a2627\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_8PYYnuoZP8</a>"},{"pid":"5444a89c4bf272fed9c0c02e81c5fb4c870471dd","tid":918126,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"如果用projection嘅概念<br />\n<br />\n三維做投影會變成二維<br />\n<br />\n同理一件四維物件嘅投影就係三維<br />\n<br />\n但因為我地三維世界生物 只靠投影係冇可能明白四維<br />\n<br />\n另一個例子係<br />\n<br />\n宜家喺張紙上面畫個圈再放個銀仔入去<br />\n<br />\n二維生物唔可能由圈外望入圈內 亦都唔可能拎個銀仔出來 但三維生物就可以<br />\n<br />\n四維對三維同理"},{"pid":"7978b3088551aff0325ca009f8f6740a03abe9dc","tid":918126,"uid":39297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"現實無4維 只存在3維 <br />\n或者有人會將時間當係第4維<br />\n又唔可以話錯 係數學上的而且確係可以接受<br />\n情況就係(a,b,c) 3維座標顯示位置<br />\n再加多個t 變（a,b,c,t) 顯示埋時間<br />\n但如果以圖像既層面上去理解<br />\n要顯示4維就要搵1支垂直於我哋世界既vector<br />\n建構於3維世界上就係4維<br />\n<br />\n我記得之前玩過呢個app係教人點理解4維空間<br />\nDrew Olbrich 的「四維空間」 <br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%9B%9B%E7%B6%AD%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93/id504201783?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E9%2596%2593%2Fid504201783%3Fmt%3D8&d=kPlvPdLcVkc%2Fw3cbopP%2FZpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=10eda0ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%9B%9B%E7%B6%AD%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93/id504201783?mt=8</a><br />\n要用鬥雞眼去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a403c455d0aa5a18a1171ac2120be38228421f","tid":918126,"uid":175523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"高維係數學家嘅玩具<br />\n比較低維度（四五六七）嘅空間有時會畀物理佬順手攞來用<br />\n但係唔好過度想像<br />\n空間來講三維就足夠描述大部分現象"},{"pid":"b1a9d24cc97fb77412c0dc022d608a4f926f83f7","tid":918126,"uid":170886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"268c030b7091ab8df84a5c39b8fae34516e5723f","tid":918126,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d10dea9432a3cc13646197ca573f40ee7348968","tid":918126,"uid":129658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"未必，可能係關理解事<br />\n即係佢可能同時存在響我地第3維度但人類未有能力/靈感去睇到/感受到<br />\n佢哋行既時間同速度同我地唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"如果我地連2維都感受唔到 <br />\n我諗唔同維數可能係互不相容的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:59:57.000Z","msg":"吓,我地會連低維度都感受唔到咖?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c740dbffcc105e329a0c93e22f1db49188be2a51","tid":918126,"uid":81094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"最簡單偽四維視覺，就係火影入邊的白眼<br />\n可以睇到360度同埋同時可以睇到物件的入邊同外邊<br />\n四維望落去三維就係咁樣"}]}